{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2427310/extras/Cabe\u00e7alho_Pronto.png?t=1738407926\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2427310/extras/Clara_Gif_2.gif?t=1738407926\" />Welcome to the Early Access of Heroes of Noname!<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2427310/extras/Aris_Gif.gif?t=1738407926\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">During Early Access, you'll have the opportunity to be a part of the game's development and even leave your mark on it, with your name in the credits or an in-game tribute based on your contributions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2427310/extras/ilustracao4Fix.png?t=1738407926\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Heroes of Noname is an RPG focused on exploration and combat. Explore a massive, ever-expanding world. Recruit unique characters. Find and combine various items to customize your characters. Multiple minigames and seasonal content. Join our Discord and become a part of our growing community! Share your experience, report bugs, and send suggestions to help us build this world together with the community.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2427310/extras/Protags.png?t=1738407926\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Still planning an english version...</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2427310/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738407926","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2427310/page.bg.jpg?t=1738407926","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/